dct_description_sm: Diagram showing how sections are numbered in each township.
Shows land for sale, railroads, 20-30 mile limits for railroad and military road grants, tunnels, waterways, marshland, springs, saw mills.
Text under "Explanations" and "Terms and conditions" regarding land shown, purchasing, etc.
Railroad extends to California, dating this after 1887, when work on the railroad was finished.
